title: You Can Draw It in Just 30 Minutes by Mark Kistler (.epub)+
description:
You Can Draw It in Just 30 Minutes: See It and Sketch It in a Half-Hour or Less by Mark Kistler

Requirements: .ePub, .AZW3 reader

Overview: Emmy Award-winning and longtime PBS host Mark Kistler is back with You Can Draw It in Just 30 Minutes, the sequel to his hugely popular You Can Draw in 30 Days. Take a 30-minute creativity break and be amazed at what you accomplish! Learn to draw 25 different everyday objects--each completed in just half an hour--with step-by-step illustrations and friendly, personality-filled instructions for each lesson.

Genre: Non-Fiction > General | Drawing
